{"tid":2197903,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"前天文台長去信特首促撤張宇人行會職務 及要求佢道歉","createTime":"2020-09-11T03:21:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-11T07:01:09.000Z","uid":22556,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"d706f94876d0fcebd725587e2bbedd4165fd25a7","tid":2197903,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T03:21:52.000Z","msg":"昨日（10日）更在電台節目暗批政府官員扮專家。天文台前台長林超英即日去信行政長官林鄭月娥，投訴張宇人屢在公開場合批評政府施政和侮辱官員，與行政會成員身份不匹配，促請林鄭立即撤掉張宇人的行會職務，並指導他向官員和公務員道歉。<br />\n<br />\n林超英表示，行會成員必須支持政府施政，有意見應在會議中表達，不應在會外說三道四，張宇人嚴重違反作為行政會議成員應有之義。他批評張宇人言行不配當行政會議成員，要求林鄭立即撤掉張宇人的行會職務，並指導張向官員和公務員道歉，「否則官員和公務員再在你麾下盡忠職守，遺禍不淺。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200911/K7BE7AQASJDIVOX6LFR7XCATLE/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2LTDUHAmCbhPlDXd9nY6lY7qVX4oRlhaf_4EARSn6jO7yawYqpp5fIHpE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200911%2FK7BE7AQASJDIVOX6LFR7XCATLE%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2LTDUHAmCbhPlDXd9nY6lY7qVX4oRlhaf_4EARSn6jO7yawYqpp5fIHpE&d=u5s3JLQ1HZhTjCUFZ9m1FD2nqaxvu5zgGSEBmbQkQbg%3D&h=7114ce97\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200911%2FK7BE7AQASJDIVOX6LFR7XCATLE%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2LTDUHAmCbhPlDXd9nY6lY7qVX4oRlhaf_4EARSn6jO7yawYqpp5fIHpE&h=91ddf48d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200911/K7BE7AQASJDIVOX6LFR7XCATLE/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2LTDUHAmCbhPlDXd9nY6lY7qVX4oRlhaf_4EARSn6jO7yawYqpp5fIHpE</a>"},{"pid":"b31545be7d5f53380dbb0cd381941d12f1ca658b","tid":2197903,"uid":38904,"like":2,"disli